(44, 20, 17, 59, 5, 14, 14, 'elders of the church', 'Role of Church Elders', 'Both passages emphasize the role of elders in the church. Acts 20:17 mentions calling the elders, while James 5:14 instructs the sick to call for the elders for prayer.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 17, 60, 5, 1, 1, 'elders of the church', 'Connection of Church Elders', 'This connection highlights the role of elders in the church. Both passages emphasize the importance of elders and their responsibilities within the Christian community.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 17, 63, 1, 1, 1, 'the elder', 'Connection of Elders and Love', 'This connection highlights the role of ''the elder'' in both passages, emphasizing leadership and care within the church community. Both passages reflect a concern for the spiritual well-being of the church and its members.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 18, 52, 1, 5, 6, NULL, 'Connection of Conduct and Influence', 'Both passages emphasize the manner of conduct of the speakers among their audiences. Acts 20:18 highlights the speaker''s consistent behavior, while 1 Thessalonians 1:5-6 reflects how this conduct influenced the recipients'' response to the gospel.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 18, 44, 18, 19, 19, 'I have been with you at all seasons', 'Paul''s Ministry in Ephesus', 'Both passages emphasize Paul''s presence in Ephesus and his engagement with the community. Acts 20:18 reflects on his manner of being with them, while Acts 18:19 shows his initial arrival and reasoning in the synagogue.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 18, 44, 19, 1, 1, 'I came into Asia', 'Paul''s Journey to Ephesus', 'This connection highlights Paul''s arrival in Ephesus, where he begins his ministry. Both passages emphasize the significance of Paul''s actions and presence in the region.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 18, 53, 3, 7, 9, 'Ye know, from the first day', 'Examples of Conduct in Ministry', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of behavior and work ethic in ministry. Acts 20:18 highlights Paul''s consistent conduct, while 2 Thessalonians 3:7-9 illustrates the example set by Paul and his companions in laboring diligently.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 18, 47, 1, 12, 12, 'what manner I have been with you', 'Sincerity in Conduct', 'Both passages emphasize the manner of conduct in ministry. Acts 20:18 speaks of how Paul was with the believers, while 2 Corinthians 1:12 highlights the sincerity and simplicity of their conversation.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 18, 47, 6, 3, 11, 'what manner I have been with you', 'Ministry and Endurance in Affliction', 'Both passages emphasize the nature of ministry through enduring hardships and maintaining integrity. Acts 20:18 speaks to the manner of Paul''s conduct, while 2 Corinthians 6:3-11 details the trials faced by ministers.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 18, 52, 2, 1, 10, 'what manner I have been with you', 'Behavior Among Believers', 'Both passages emphasize the manner of conduct among believers. Acts 20:18 speaks of how Paul behaved at all seasons, while 1 Thessalonians 2:10 describes his holy and just behavior among the Thessalonians.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 19, 51, 3, 24, 24, NULL, 'Service and Reward Connection', 'Both passages emphasize serving the Lord, with Acts highlighting humility and trials, while Colossians assures believers of a reward for their service. This connection highlights the importance of dedication in serving Christ amidst challenges.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 19, 45, 12, 11, 11, 'serving the Lord', 'Serving the Lord Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of serving the Lord. Acts 20:19 highlights humility and perseverance in service, while Romans 12:11 encourages fervency and diligence in serving.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 19, 47, 2, 4, 4, 'with many tears', 'Affliction and Tears Connection', 'Both passages emphasize serving and writing with ''many tears'' amid affliction. This connection highlights the emotional depth and struggles faced by the authors in their ministry.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 19, 44, 20, 3, 3, 'lying in wait of the Jews', 'Connection of Persecution and Humility', 'Both passages emphasize the challenges faced by Paul, particularly the ''lying in wait of the Jews.'' This connection highlights the theme of perseverance in the face of opposition and the humility required in serving the Lord.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 19, 47, 4, 7, 11, 'temptations', 'Endurance in Suffering', 'Both passages emphasize the experience of suffering and perseverance in the face of trials. Acts 20:19 mentions ''temptations'' and ''tears,'' while 2 Corinthians 4:7-11 describes being ''troubled,'' ''persecuted,'' and ''cast down,'' yet remaining resilient.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 19, 24, 13, 17, 17, 'with many tears', 'Connection of Tears and Humility', 'This connection highlights the theme of weeping and humility in both passages. Acts 20:19 mentions ''many tears'' in the context of serving with humility, while Jeremiah 13:17 speaks of weeping due to pride and the plight of the Lord''s flock.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 19, 44, 14, 19, 20, 'temptations', 'Persecution and Resilience in Ministry', 'Both passages emphasize the trials faced by Paul, including physical harm and emotional distress. Acts 20:19 mentions ''temptations'' and ''tears,'' while Acts 14:19-20 describes Paul being stoned, highlighting his perseverance in serving the Lord despite adversity.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 20, 44, 20, 27, 27, 'have shewed you, and have taught you', 'Teaching and Counsel Connection', 'This connection highlights the commitment to teaching, as seen in both passages. Acts 20:20 emphasizes showing and teaching, while Acts 20:27 speaks to declaring all the counsel of God.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 20, 44, 5, 42, 42, 'from house to house', 'Teaching and Preaching Connection', 'This connection highlights the commitment to teaching and preaching Jesus Christ in both passages. Acts 20:20 emphasizes teaching publicly and from house to house, while Acts 5:42 mentions teaching daily in the temple and every house.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 20, 55, 4, 2, 2, 'have shewed you, and have taught you', 'Teaching and Preaching Connection', 'This connection highlights the emphasis on teaching and preaching in both passages. Acts 20:20 mentions showing and teaching, while 2 Timothy 4:2 calls for preaching and exhortation.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 20, 51, 1, 28, 28, 'have shewed you, and have taught you', 'Teaching and Warning Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of teaching and warning others. Acts 20:20 mentions teaching publicly and from house to house, while Colossians 1:28 highlights warning and teaching every man in all wisdom.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 20, 5, 4, 5, 5, 'have shewed you, and have taught you', 'Teaching and Instruction Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of teaching and instruction. Both passages emphasize the importance of imparting knowledge and statutes to others, whether in a communal or personal setting.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 20, 19, 40, 9, 10, 'have shewed you, and have taught you', 'Preaching and Declaration of Righteousness', 'This connection highlights the act of publicly declaring righteousness and truth. Both passages emphasize the importance of teaching and not concealing God''s message.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
